Title:
SUD's Dumaloy Album Tour | 10.15.22

STORY TIME ??

As most of you already know, nagsimula talaga kami as a cover band, at isa sa go-to songs namin that time ay "Sila" by SUD. Hindi mawawala sa band repertoire namin dati 'yun, kasi sobrang enjoy na enjoy kami tugtugin 'yun. Ultimo yung sax parts ginagaya namin using Cedric's handy-dandy melodica, since wala naman kaming sax talaga. 

Nakakakilig lang isipin na ngayon, we were lucky enough to be given the chance na makasama sa album tour nila. This gig really meant a lot para sa amin as a band. Thank you SUD! Maraming salamat din sa lahat ng mga nanood at sumuporta. 

Special thanks to Warner Music Philippines, All Goods Productions, Milenya PH, Leanne & Naara, and TONEEJAY, sobrang solid niyo pong lahat! ????

Check video sa comments section! HAHAHA

??: Gilliane Bernabe

Maraming Salamat!! ????

SUGARCANE just reached 100k monthly listeners on Spotify! Words cannot express how much this means to us. 

This would not be possible without our Warner Music Philippines Family, and our beloved SUGARCANE Family. Success nating lahat ?to! Makakaasa kayo na mas huhusayan pa namin. Mahal na mahal namin kayo.??
See you!! ????

Join us this October 15, 7 PM, at Milenya PH for SUD?s Dumaloy Album Tour!

We will be sharing the stage with SUD, Leanne & Naara, and TONEEJAY. Kitakits! Excited kaming makita at makasama kayo. ??
1 Million Streams na ang "Gunita" ????
Description:
1 Million Streams na ang "Gunita" ????

Two of our songs, "Kung Maging Akin ka" & "Gunita", reached a million streams this year. What a year this has been for us! Maraming Salamat! Sobrang na-appreciate namin lahat ng suporta niyo. 

PS. Two songs din back-to-back ang dapat niyong abangan next year. ??

Stream here: https://sugarcane.lnk.to/gunita

"Sinehan" is a melancholic song about two lovers on the verge of a breakup, realizing that they are not meant for each other. The overall message of the song expresses the sorrow of letting go, acknowledging that some love stories just aren't destined to last. 

In its entirety, "Sinehan" is a song that captures the complexities of love, letting go, and the transcendent effect of acceptance. It serves as a reminder that even in the midst of heartbreak, there can be wonders in the acknowledgment that some love stories are meant to be cherished as fleeting moments on the grand cinema screen of life.

"Leonora" is a heart-wrenching tribute to the tragic love story of Jose Rizal and his teenage love, Leonor Rivera. The song captures the essence of the classic tale of forbidden love, as Leonor's mother disapproves of Rizal's work as a propagandist, ultimately tearing the couple apart. 

With its powerful lyrics and emotive melodies, "Leonora" paints a picture of a love that could have been, but ultimately never was, and is sure to leave a lasting impression on listeners, as they relate to the universal themes of unrequited love, heartbreak, and the struggles of following one's passions.

Lyricist: Froilan Bautista
Composer: Cedric Angeles 
Recorded by: Cedric Angeles, Dennis Celis, & Rene Serna (Spryta Recording Studio)

?? IMPORTANT ANNOUNCEMENT ??
(From Rakrakan Festival)

Dear Rakrakan Festival Community,

We regret to inform you that the highly anticipated Rakrakan Festival event, originally scheduled for June 10 & 11, 2023, at Clark Global City, will be postponed. The decision comes in light of the impending weather conditions of heavy rains, strong winds and thunderstorms not only during the event itself but during the upcoming days when we are scheduled to do our ingress.

As an event centered around the theme of Peace, Love, & Music, the well-being of our attendees, artists, and staff remains our top priority. ????? 

We want to express our deepest apologies to all of you who have been eagerly anticipating Rakrakan Festival. We understand the disappointment and inconvenience this may cause, but again, your safety is out utmost priority.

Rest assured that your 2023 Rakrakan tickets will remain valid for the rescheduled date. We appreciate your patience and continued support during this challenging time. For those unable to attend the rescheduled event, we will provide information on how to request a refund through our designated channels.

We are actively working to secure a new date that will allow us to deliver an exceptional Rakrakan Festival experience, staying true to the theme of Peace, Love, & Music. We appreciate your understanding and continued support as we prioritize the safety, unity, and celebration of Peace, Love, & Music for all attendees.

Thank you for being a part of the Rakrakan Festival community. Your unwavering support means the world to us!

Stay safe, stay connected, and let the music unite us.

Yours sincerely,
Rakrakan Festival

"Paalam, Leonora" is a heart-wrenching and intimate acoustic rendition of the original song, "Leonora". It tells the tragic love story of Jose Rizal and his greatest love, Leonor Rivera, with a more sorrowful and introspective approach.

The stripped-down arrangement of "Paalam, Leonora" puts the focus on the emotional weight of the lyrics and the beautiful melody. The added exclusive ending/outro verse conveys a sense of acceptance of a love that was not meant to be, making the song even more poignant.
